<PB REF="023387_0226_0FBF64993A334EA8">
<HEAD>A CONCISE SYSTEM OF PRACTICAL ARITHMETIC.</HEAD>
<DIV2 TYPE="section">
<HEAD>INTRODUCTION.</HEAD>
<P>ARITHMETIC is the art or &s;cience of numbering; for as magnitude is the &s;ubject of Geometry, &s;o is multitude, or numbers, the &s;ubject of Arithmetic; the whole art of which, depends chiefly, upon the thorough knowledge of the five follow|ing Rules (all the other rules being com|pounded of them) viz. Numeration, Addi|tion, Subtraction, Multiplication, and Di|vi&s;ion:</P>
</DIV2>
<DIV2 TYPE="section">
<PB N="225" REF="023387_0227_0FBF649A81F294B8">
