<ITEM>10 Cents make 1 Dime,</ITEM>
<ITEM>10 Dimes make 1 Dollar,</ITEM>
<ITEM>10 Dollars make 1 Eagle.</ITEM>
</LIST></P>
<P>Note. E. &s;tands for Eagle, Dl. for Dollar, Dm. for Dime, Cn. for Cent, and Ml. for Mills.</P>
